Acordam, ainda, por unanimidade, julgando o recurso de revista, na forma do art. 897, &sect; 7&ordm;, da CLT, dele conhecer, apenas quanto ao tema afeto &agrave; responsabilidade subsidi&aacute;ria do ente p&uacute;blico, por viola&ccedil;&atilde;o do art. 71, &sect; 1&ordm;, da Lei n&ordm; 8.666/93, e, no m&eacute;rito, dar-lhe provimento para absolver o recorrente da condena&ccedil;&atilde;o imposta como respons&aacute;vel subsidi&aacute;rio.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 5.0cm; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">Prejudicado o exame dos temas recursais remanescentes. <span style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;">(Processo n&ordm; RR-117000-10.2011.5.21.0007, </span>Relator Min. Walmir Oliveira da Costa, Recorrente(s) ESTADO DO RIO GRANDE DO NORTE, Procurador Dr. Ana Cl&aacute;udia Bulh&otilde;es Porpino de Macedo(OAB: null), Recorrido(s) MARIA GORETE GOMES,<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>Advogada Dra. Erika Hackradt Dias(OAB: null) Recorrido(s) MOVIMENTO DE INTEGRA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O E ORIENTA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O SOCIAL - MEIOS).</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 5.0cm; text-indent: 35.4pt;"><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-weight: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 5.0cm; text-indent: 5.0cm; tab-stops: 72.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 5.0cm; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><a name="tempEmenta"></a><a name="Ementa"></a><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">AGRAVO DE INSTRUMENTO EM RECURSO DE REVISTA. RESPONSABILIDADE SUBSIDI&Aacute;RIA. ENTE P&Uacute;BLICO. N&Atilde;O CONFIGURA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O.</span></strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;"> Diante da ofensa ao art. 71, &sect; 1.&ordm;, da Lei n.&ordm; 8.666/93, determina-se o processamento do Recurso de Revista. <strong>Agravo de Instrumento a que se d&aacute; provimento. RECURSO DE REVISTA. RESPONSABILIDADE SUBSIDI&Aacute;RIA. ENTE P&Uacute;BLICO. N&Atilde;O CONFIGURA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O.</strong> Para que seja autorizada a responsabilidade subsidi&aacute;ria da Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica pelo inadimplemento das obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es trabalhistas por parte da empresa contratada conforme o disposto na Lei n.&ordm; 8.666/93, deve ser demonstrada a sua conduta omissiva no que se refere &agrave; fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o do cumprimento das obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es relativas aos encargos trabalhistas. Esse, ali&aacute;s, foi o entendimento esposado pelo Supremo Tribunal Federal, que em recente decis&atilde;o (ADC 16 - 24/11/2010), ao declarar a constitucionalidade do art. 71, &sect; 1.&ordm;, da Lei n.&ordm; 8.666/93, asseverou que, constatada a culpa "in vigilando", gera-se a responsabilidade subsidi&aacute;ria da Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica. N&atilde;o estando comprovada a omiss&atilde;o culposa do ente em rela&ccedil;&atilde;o &agrave; fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o quanto ao cumprimento das obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es trabalhistas, n&atilde;o h&aacute; de se falar em responsabilidade subsidi&aacute;ria. <strong>Recurso de Revista conhecido e provido.</strong></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 5.0cm; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a name="tempRelatorio"></a>Vistos, relatados e discutidos estes autos de <a name="TipoProc"></a>Recurso de Revista n.&ordm; <strong>TST-RR-132700-38.2011.5.21.0003</strong>, em que &eacute; Recorrente <strong>ESTADO DO RIO GRANDE DO NORTE</strong> e s&atilde;o Recorridos <strong>JANILSON LIMA DOS SANTOS </strong>e<strong> MOVIMENTO DE INTEGRA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O E ORIENTA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O SOCIAL - MEIOS</strong>.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 144.0pt; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">De mais a mais, importa registrar o disposto no </span></strong><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">item V, da s&uacute;mula 331, onde resta estabelecido a necessidade de comprova&ccedil;&atilde;o efetiva da aus&ecirc;ncia de fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o do ente p&uacute;blico contratante de servi&ccedil;os terceirizados, para, ent&atilde;o, poder ser responsabilizado subsidiariamente pelos d&eacute;bitos trabalhistas da empresa contratada. </span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 144.0pt; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">In casu</span></em></strong><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">, a citada prova irrefut&aacute;vel resta ausente. Assim, a decis&atilde;o recorrida, <em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">d.m.v.,</em> dever&aacute; ser reformada para isentar o DETRAN/RN da responsabilidade subsidi&aacute;ria que lhe fora imposta pelo tribunal de origem.</span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Da an&aacute;lise da decis&atilde;o recorrida, constata-se que a raz&atilde;o da condena&ccedil;&atilde;o subsidi&aacute;ria do Detran/RN no pagamento de parcelas trabalhistas deveu-se &agrave; aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o da teoria da culpa <em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">in vigilando</em> (S&uacute;mula 331, V, do TST).</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Tal argumento foi recha&ccedil;ado no dia 24.11.2010, no julgamento da <strong>ADC 16</strong>, onde o Pleno do Supremo Tribunal Federal reconheceu a constitucionalidade do preceptivo do art. 71, &sect; 1&deg;, da Lei 8.666/93, de onde ressai a inescond&iacute;vel necessidade de reforma do julgado, com vistas &agrave; exclus&atilde;o do ente p&uacute;blico da lide ou de sua responsabilidade subsidi&aacute;ria, sob pena de viola&ccedil;&atilde;o ao disposto no art. 102, &sect;2&ordm;, da CF/88, que estabelece o efeito vinculante das decis&otilde;es proferidas em sede de a&ccedil;&atilde;o declarat&oacute;ria de constitucionalidade.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: 12.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Com efeito, a mera inadimpl&ecirc;ncia do contratado n&atilde;o pode transferir &agrave; Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica a responsabilidade pelo pagamento dos encargos, devendo, assim, <strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">restar devidamente provado</strong>, nos autos, a omiss&atilde;o da Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica, na obriga&ccedil;&atilde;o de fiscalizar as obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es do contratado.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">O fato &eacute; que, &agrave; m&iacute;ngua de prova nos autos quanto &agrave; culpa <em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">in vigilando</em> do litisconsorte, acerca do inadimplemento das verbas ora postuladas, ressai inescond&iacute;vel necessidade de reforma do julgado, com vistas &agrave; exclus&atilde;o do ente p&uacute;blico da lide ou de sua responsabilidade subsidi&aacute;ria, sob pena de viola&ccedil;&atilde;o ao disposto no art. 102, &sect;2&ordm;, da CF/88, que estabelece o efeito vinculante das decis&otilde;es proferidas em sede de a&ccedil;&atilde;o declarat&oacute;ria de constitucionalidade.</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><strong>Enfim, a</strong></span><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "> instru&ccedil;&atilde;o processual, quanto ao controle e fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o na execu&ccedil;&atilde;o do contrato de presta&ccedil;&atilde;o de servi&ccedil;os, por parte da Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o, &eacute; imperativo para se apurar a responsabilidade por culpa e, assim, condenar-se subsidiariamente a Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica, o que, de fato, inocorreu.</span></strong></p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Como se pode verificar, a lide gravita em torno da possibilidade de o DETRAN/RN ser responsabilizado, ainda que subsidiariamente, pelo pagamento dos encargos trabalhistas decorrentes da execu&ccedil;&atilde;o de contrato administrativo de presta&ccedil;&atilde;o de servi&ccedil;os, quando da inadimpl&ecirc;ncia da empresa contratada.</span></p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Nesse aspecto, n&atilde;o h&aacute; como aplicar a s&uacute;mula 331-TST, que contraria o disposto no art. 71, &sect;1&ordm;, da Lei 8.666/93, <span style="text-decoration: underline;">CUJA CONSTITUCIONALIDADE FOI RECONHECIDA PELO STF, NO JULGAMENTO DA ADC 16, NO DIA 24.11.2010, sob pena de viola&ccedil;&atilde;o ao disposto no art. 102, &sect;2&ordm;, da CF/88, que imp&otilde;e a obrigat&oacute;ria observ&acirc;ncia dos &oacute;rg&atilde;os p&uacute;blicos administrativos e judiciais no que toca &agrave;s decis&otilde;es proferidas em sede de ADI e ADC, atrav&eacute;s do estabelecimento do efeito vinculante dos aludidos julgados.</span></span></p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Por outro lado, d</span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">e acordo com a s&uacute;mula 331, V, somente nos casos em que seja <strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">comprovada</span></strong> a culpa <em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">in vigilando, </em>pode o ente p&uacute;blico, contratante de servi&ccedil;os terceirizados, ser responsabilizado pelo pagamento dos d&eacute;bitos trabalhistas.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 144.0pt;"><em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">In casu, </span></em><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">basta uma breve an&aacute;lise sobre a ata da audi&ecirc;ncia e na documenta&ccedil;&atilde;o adunada aos autos para se concluir pela inexist&ecirc;ncia de qualquer instru&ccedil;&atilde;o, quanto mais de uma que seja conclusiva pela culpa <em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">in vigilando </em>do ente p&uacute;blico. Nada foi produzido a respeito, da&iacute; por que a decis&atilde;o recorrida contraria a nova reda&ccedil;&atilde;o dada &agrave; s&uacute;mula 331, pelo e. TST.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Como visto, o julgado recorrido n&atilde;o demonstrou, atrav&eacute;s de meios de prova, que houve a culpa <em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">in vigilando </em>do litisconsorte ora recorrente.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Nesse aspecto, de acordo com a s&uacute;mula 331, deve restar cabalmente demonstrada a aus&ecirc;ncia de fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o do <strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">ente p&uacute;blico contratante de servi&ccedil;os terceirizados</span></strong>, para, assim, poder ser responsabilizado subsidiariamente pelos d&eacute;bitos trabalhistas da empresa contratada.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 5.0cm; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Ainda que n&atilde;o se acate a argumenta&ccedil;&atilde;o acima, <strong>importa consignar que, em decis&atilde;o recente, o v. TST consignou, no Agravo de Instrumento n&deg; 138540-97.2009.5.21.0003 (pub. 01/04/2011), que a responsabiliza&ccedil;&atilde;o subsidi&aacute;ria estatal </strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">somente poder&aacute; ocorrer quanto este tenha agido, comprovadamente, de forma omissiva quando da fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o do cumprimento das referidas obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es. Tal conduta deve estar demonstrada nos autos, porquanto n&atilde;o h&aacute; de se cogitar de imposi&ccedil;&atilde;o de responsabilidade objetiva &agrave; Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica com amparo no art. 37, &sect; 6&deg;, da Carta Magna.</span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 144.0pt; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Igualmente, decidiu-se no RR - 160900-11.2009.5.21.0008, julgado em 25/05/11.</span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 144.0pt; line-height: 150%;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Portanto, inexiste prova de que houve a culpa <em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">in vigilando</em></span></strong><em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "> </span></em><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">do litisconsorte, &ocirc;nus que competia &agrave; recorrida, nos termos do art.818, da CLT e<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>373, I, do CPC e n&atilde;o ao DETRAN/RN. <strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">Nesse aspecto, tal situa&ccedil;&atilde;o n&atilde;o se presume.</strong></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>O fato &eacute; que, inexistem raz&otilde;es de fato informadas na senten&ccedil;a e a responsabiliza&ccedil;&atilde;o subsidi&aacute;ria n&atilde;o se presume, especialmente ap&oacute;s a prola&ccedil;&atilde;o da decis&atilde;o, pelo STF, na ADC 16.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">Atente-se, novamente, para o fato de que, em momento algum, a s&uacute;mula 331, TST, ou o julgamento proferido na ADC, determinou que o &ocirc;nus da prova da fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o pertence ao litisconsorte. Ora, o Ju&iacute;zo de 1&ordm; grau, atrav&eacute;s da correta e devida instru&ccedil;&atilde;o, poderia, perfeitamente, descobrir como os fatos ocorreram com os depoimentos dos prepostos da empresa reclamada e do litisconsorte e, at&eacute; mesmo, de testemunhas de ambas as partes ou requisitadas pelo Ju&iacute;zo.</strong></span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Assim, como dito, a senten&ccedil;a recorrida n&atilde;o observou as altera&ccedil;&otilde;es promovidas pela decis&atilde;o proferida na ADC 16 e pela s&uacute;mula 331, especialmente no que se refere &agrave; <strong>necessidade de ser cabalmente demonstrada a culpa <em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">in vigilando </em>do ente p&uacute;blico, para que possa ser responsabilizado pelo pagamento das parcelas trabalhistas.</strong></span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 5.0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;"> </span>De mais a mais, impende considerar, ainda, que, ao contr&aacute;rio do que determina a s&uacute;mula 331, do TST, que estabelece a responsabiliza&ccedil;&atilde;o estatal em raz&atilde;o de culpa <em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">in vigilando </em>(QUE N&Atilde;O RESTOU COMPROVADA NA ESP&Eacute;CIE DOS AUTOS), o e. STF pacificou, SEM RESSALVAS, o entendimento no sentido de que N&Atilde;O &Eacute; CAB&Iacute;VEL A RESPONSABILIZA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O DOS ENTES P&Uacute;BLICOS, PELO PAGAMENTO DE PARCELAS TRABALHISTAS DECORRENTES DE CONTRATOS ADMINISTRATIVOS, veja-se:</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2"><span style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;">EMENTA: AGRAVO REGIMENTAL NA RECLAMA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O. ADMINISTRATIVO. RESPONSABILIDADE SUBSIDI&Aacute;RIA. IMPOSSIBILIDADE DE TRANSFERIR PARA A ADMINISTRA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O P&Uacute;BLICA A OBRIGA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O DE PAGAR OS ENCARGOS TRABALHISTAS RESULTANTES DA EXECU&Ccedil;&Atilde;O DE CONTRATO ADMINISTRATIVO. CONSTITUCIONALIDADE DO ART. 71, &sect; 1&ordm;, DA LEI N. 8.666/1993 RECONHECIDA NA A&Ccedil;&Atilde;O DECLARAT&Oacute;RIA DE CONSTITUCIONALIDADE N. <span style="color: red;">16.</span> PRECEDENTES. AGRAVO REGIMENTAL AO QUAL SE NEGA PROVIMENTO. (STF, Pleno, Rcl 12926 AgR / PR - PARAN&Aacute;, AG.REG. NA RECLAMA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O,</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;"><br /> </span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;">Relator(a):&nbsp; Min. C&Aacute;RMEN L&Uacute;CIA, publ. em 09.02.2012)</span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2"><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 5.0cm; tab-stops: 5.0cm;"><strong><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Nesse cen&aacute;rio, n&atilde;o interessa se houve, ou n&atilde;o, culpa <em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">in vigilando </em>ou <em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">in eligendo</em>: o art. 71, &sect;1&ordm;, da lei 8666/93, que teve sua constitucionalidade reconhecida no julgamento da ADC 16, incide sobre a esp&eacute;cie dos autos, isentando o recorrente quanto ao pagamento de qualquer parcela trabalhista decorrente de contrato ou de conv&ecirc;nio administrativo.</span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 5.0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;"> </span>Portanto, &eacute; inquestion&aacute;vel a incompatibilidade existente entre o aludido dispositivo, de reconhecida constitucionalidade, e a s&uacute;mula 331, do TST, especialmente no item que responsabiliza os entes p&uacute;blicos pelo pagamento de parcelas trabalhistas decorrentes de contratos administrativos. Tal conclus&atilde;o se encontra bem revelada no ac&oacute;rd&atilde;o acima reproduzido, proferido pelo e. STF.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Pelo exposto, tem-se que a decis&atilde;o recorrida, assim como a s&uacute;mula 331 - TST, contraria o art. 71, &sect;1&ordm;, da lei 8.666/93, e o art. 102, &sect;2&ordm;, da CF.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 144.0pt; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">A senten&ccedil;a contraria, por conseguinte, os arts. 818, da CLT, e 333, I, do CPC.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Merece reforma a decis&atilde;o tamb&eacute;m no que tange &agrave; condena&ccedil;&atilde;o </span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">no recolhimento das contribui&ccedil;&otilde;es previdenci&aacute;rias.</span></p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 144.0pt; line-height: 150%; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">No caso dos autos, descabe a condena&ccedil;&atilde;o subsidi&aacute;ria do recorrente no que toca &agrave;s contribui&ccedil;&otilde;es previdenci&aacute;rias, que t&ecirc;m natureza tribut&aacute;ria, haja vista a s&uacute;mula 331, em seu inciso IV, estabelecer a responsabilidade subsidi&aacute;ria unicamente quanto &agrave;s obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es trabalhistas</span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Portanto, resta evidente o <em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">error in judicando</em> da decis&atilde;o.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><strong><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">IV - DA INCOMPET&Ecirc;NCIA DA JUSTI&Ccedil;A DO TRABALHO PARA IMPOR RESPONSABILIDADE A ENTE P&Uacute;BLICO CONTRATANTE </span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">Sob esse aspecto, o </strong></span><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">DETRAN/RN<span style="color: black;"> suscita, novamente, a preliminar predita.</span></span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>A compet&ecirc;ncia da Justi&ccedil;a do Trabalho foi bem delimitada pela CF/88, principalmente ap&oacute;s o advento da Emenda Constitucional n&ordm; 45/2004, nos seguintes termos:</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">"Art. 114. - Compete &agrave; Justi&ccedil;a do Trabalho processar e julgar:</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">I - as a&ccedil;&otilde;es oriundas da rela&ccedil;&atilde;o de trabalho, abrangidos os entes de direito p&uacute;blico externo e da administra&ccedil;&atilde;o p&uacute;blica direta e indireta da Uni&atilde;o, dos Estados, do Distrito Federal e dos Munic&iacute;pios;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">(...)</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">IX - outras controv&eacute;rsias decorrentes da rela&ccedil;&atilde;o de trabalho, na forma da lei;".</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: black;"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Somente foram reproduzidos os incisos I e IX, do art. 114, da CF/88, uma vez que apenas eles poderiam, em tese, guardar conformidade com o tema ora debatido.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>A natureza do ajuste celebrado entre a Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica e a empresa terceirizada, n&atilde;o restam d&uacute;vidas, &eacute; de contrato eminentemente administrativo.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Como bem ensina Leonardo Jub&eacute; de Moura<a style="mso-footnote-id: ftn1;" name="_ftnref1" href="#_ftn1"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="mso-ansi-font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%;"><span style="mso-special-character: footnote;"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">[1]</span></span></span></span></span></a>,</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">"...n&atilde;o h&aacute;, <em>in casu, </em>rela&ccedil;&atilde;o trabalhista entre a administra&ccedil;&atilde;o e os empregados da empresa contratada. H&aacute;, isto sim, contrato de presta&ccedil;&atilde;o de servi&ccedil;os, entre empresa e ente p&uacute;blico, regido por normas de Direito Administrativo e de Direito Civil - nada que diga com Direito do Trabalho."</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: black;"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Tratam-se de rela&ccedil;&otilde;es distintas, titularizadas por pessoas distintas.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>No contrato de presta&ccedil;&atilde;o de servi&ccedil;os, os celebrantes s&atilde;o o ente p&uacute;blico e a empresa prestadora de servi&ccedil;os; por sua vez, a rela&ccedil;&atilde;o laboral &eacute; formada entre a empresa privada contratada e os respectivos empregados.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>N&atilde;o h&aacute; espa&ccedil;o para comunica&ccedil;&atilde;o entre os dois v&iacute;nculos.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Na forma&ccedil;&atilde;o do contrato de trabalho, n&atilde;o h&aacute; a participa&ccedil;&atilde;o do ente p&uacute;blico na sele&ccedil;&atilde;o, na admiss&atilde;o, na dire&ccedil;&atilde;o da presta&ccedil;&atilde;o do servi&ccedil;o, no acerto da remunera&ccedil;&atilde;o e no pagamento desta.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Em s&iacute;ntese, inexiste rela&ccedil;&atilde;o de trabalho entre a Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica e os empregados prestadores de servi&ccedil;o.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Ao ente p&uacute;blico n&atilde;o interessa sequer saber quantos empregados ser&atilde;o destinados &agrave; presta&ccedil;&atilde;o dos servi&ccedil;os terceirizados, mas sim a efici&ecirc;ncia dos mesmos (servi&ccedil;os), at&eacute; porque tal princ&iacute;pio det&eacute;m <em>status </em>constitucional (art. 37, <em>caput, </em>da CF/88).</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>O contrato administrativo celebrado entre a Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica e a empresa licitante vencedora possui, notadamente, natureza diversa da rela&ccedil;&atilde;o laboral, da&iacute; porque falece &agrave;quela Justi&ccedil;a Especializada compet&ecirc;ncia, <em>in ratione materiae, </em>para apreci&aacute;-lo, quanto mais para estender responsabilidade trabalhista &agrave; Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica, decorrente do aludido ajuste administrativo.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>De acordo com o Professor Celso Ant&ocirc;nio Bandeira de Mello, </span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">"...pode-se conceituar contrato administrativo da seguinte forma: &eacute; um tipo de avenca travada entre a Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o e terceiros na qual, por for&ccedil;a de lei, de cl&aacute;usulas<span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span> pactuadas ou do tipo de objeto, a perman&ecirc;ncia do v&iacute;nculo e as condi&ccedil;&otilde;es preestabelecidas assujeitam-se a cambi&aacute;veis imposi&ccedil;&otilde;es de direito p&uacute;blico, ressalvados os interesses patrimoniais do contratante privado."<a style="mso-footnote-id: ftn2;" name="_ftnref2" href="#_ftn2"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="mso-ansi-font-size: 11.5pt;"><span style="mso-special-character: footnote;"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: ">[2]</span></span></span></span></span></a><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;"> </span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: black;"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Noutro momento<a style="mso-footnote-id: ftn3;" name="_ftnref3" href="#_ftn3"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="mso-ansi-font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%;"><span style="mso-special-character: footnote;"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">[3]</span></span></span></span></span></a>, o eminente doutrinador acentua as diferen&ccedil;as existentes entre o contrato administrativo e os pactos de natureza privada, como, p. ex., o contrato de trabalho:</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">"<strong>Peculiaridades do contrato administrativo.</strong></span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>5. Tal disciplina marca-se sobretudo (embora n&atilde;o s&oacute;) pela possibilidade de a Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o <em>instabilizar </em>o v&iacute;nculo, seja:</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; text-indent: 0cm; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 159.75pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">a)<span style="font: 7.0pt ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><em><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">alterando </span></em><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">unilateralmente o que fora pactuado a respeito das obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es do contratante;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; text-indent: 0cm; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 159.75pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">b)<span style="font: 7.0pt ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><em><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">extinguindo </span></em><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">unilateralmente o v&iacute;nculo.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">Ambas as formas de instabiliza&ccedil;&atilde;o constituem um direito da Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o, ressalvadas a identidade do objeto da aven&ccedil;a e a plena garantia dos interesses patrimoniais da outra parte.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">6. Estas prerrogativas derivariam ou da sistem&aacute;tica normativa, que protege acentuadamente determinadas atividades p&uacute;blicas, ou de 'cl&aacute;usulas contratuais' concebidas como exorbitantes. Tanto poderiam ser colhidas nos textos que diretamente regulam a mat&eacute;ria - quando existentes - como deduzidas dos princ&iacute;pios retores de certas atividades p&uacute;blicas. Vale dizer: ou se reputam <em>impl&iacute;citas</em>, seja na ordena&ccedil;&atilde;o normativa, seja no bojo do contrato, ou est&atilde;o realmente <em>expl&iacute;citas </em>na lei ou em cl&aacute;usula expressa do contrato.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">7. De conseguinte, as <em>prerrogativas </em>da Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o no chamado contrato administrativo s&atilde;o reputadas existentes por for&ccedil;a da ordena&ccedil;&atilde;o legal ou das cl&aacute;usulas exorbitantes da aven&ccedil;a. <strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Evidentemente, sua 'exorbit&acirc;ncia' ocorre em rela&ccedil;&atilde;o ao Direito Privado e consiste em abrigar disposi&ccedil;&otilde;es nele inadmiss&iacute;veis ou incomuns." </span></strong>(os destaques n&atilde;o s&atilde;o do original)</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: black;"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Eis, portanto, as raz&otilde;es por que se reputa a Justi&ccedil;a Especializada do Trabalho incompetente para apreciar o contrato administrativo e os efeitos dele decorrentes, principalmente por tratar-se de segmento especializado no ramo do Direito Privado, ao passo que a mat&eacute;ria possui natureza eminentemente p&uacute;blica.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal;"><strong><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">IV - DA ILEGITIMIDADE PASSIVA <em>AD CAUSAM</em>.</span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">O ente federativo reitera a sua ilegitimidade passiva.</strong></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 144.0pt; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Como se sabe, n&atilde;o existe previs&atilde;o legal determinando que o Estado e suas autarquias figurem no p&oacute;lo passivo da presente reclamat&oacute;ria, e o que &eacute; pior, seja condenado; uma vez que o reclamante jamais manteve contrato de trabalho com o referido Ente p&uacute;blico.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 144.0pt; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Conv&eacute;m lembrar que a empresa/contratada possui capacidade jur&iacute;dica e, <em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">in casu</em>, &eacute; a empregadora da recorrente. Portanto, &eacute; quem tem legitimidade para figurar no p&oacute;lo passivo da lide e, se for o caso, responder por eventuais cr&eacute;ditos trabalhistas do autor de forma exclusiva, haja vista, que possui personalidade jur&iacute;dica pr&oacute;pria e responde pelos seus pr&oacute;prios atos. N&atilde;o bastassem essas raz&otilde;es para decretar-se a ilegitimidade passiva do DETRAN/RN, no caso em cotejo &eacute; de se aduzir que h&aacute; total impertin&ecirc;ncia na pretens&atilde;o de imputar aos entes p&uacute;blicos responsabilidade, quando estes contratam com as empresas privadas, como &eacute; o caso dos autos, pois neste caso, como se ver&aacute; mais detidamente logo abaixo, cumpri-lhe t&atilde;o somente observar os requisitos constantes da legisla&ccedil;&atilde;o licitat&oacute;ria, de car&aacute;ter nacional.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 144.0pt; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Como se sabe, qualquer empresa contratada pela Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o atrav&eacute;s de procedimento licitat&oacute;rio deve atender aos requisitos da lei e, portanto, naturalmente, ser considerada id&ocirc;nea, de sorte que n&atilde;o se pode dizer que o DETRAN/RN agiu com culpa, na ocasi&atilde;o, por haver escolhido seu contratante, que posteriormente se tornou relapso empregador. Sem culpa, <span style="text-decoration: underline;">n&atilde;o h&aacute; falar de subsidiariedade</span>, de maneira que a exclus&atilde;o do DETRAN/RN na presente lide &eacute; medida, <em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">data venia</em>, necess&aacute;ria, posto que o mesmo n&atilde;o agiu com dolo ou m&aacute;-f&eacute;, ou ainda promoveu qualquer burla &agrave; legisla&ccedil;&atilde;o trabalhista.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 144.0pt; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Destarte, requer a <strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">exclus&atilde;o </strong>do DETRAN do RN do feito, por ser parte ileg&iacute;tima para figurar na demanda. </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">V -<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>DA NULIDADE DO CONTRATO DE TRABALHO.</span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent" style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 144.0pt; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Impende reconhecer inicialmente a total aus&ecirc;ncia de v&iacute;nculo empregat&iacute;cio do reclamantes com o DETRAN do RN, que n&atilde;o poderia, nem pode admitir o ingresso de servidores p&uacute;blicos sem que haja realiza&ccedil;&atilde;o de concurso p&uacute;blico de provas, ou de provas e t&iacute;tulos, na conformidade com o inciso II, do artigo 37 da Constitui&ccedil;&atilde;o Federal, principalmente sob a &eacute;gide da Lei Complementar 122/94, em vigor desde 01 de julho de 1994.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent" style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 72.0pt; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Sobre a mat&eacute;ria, o Colendo Tribunal Superior do Trabalho j&aacute; pacificou a jurisprud&ecirc;ncia no sentido de s&oacute; serem devidos, no contrato nulo, os sal&aacute;rios retidos.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent" style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 72.0pt; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Assim, aceitar-se a responsabiliza&ccedil;&atilde;o do DETRAN do RN, no que tange ao pagamento de diversas verbas trabalhistas, em fun&ccedil;&atilde;o de contrato de terceiriza&ccedil;&atilde;o, consubstanciaria um contra-senso, uma vez que o contrato de trabalho nulo, realizado diretamente entre a Fazenda Estadual e o empregado, s&oacute; atribui &agrave;quela a obriga&ccedil;&atilde;o de pagar o saldo de sal&aacute;rios, conforme jurisprud&ecirc;ncia esmagadora da Superior Corte Trabalhista.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent" style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 72.0pt; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Dessa forma, restam prejudicados todos os t&iacute;tulos trabalhistas postulados pelo autor, sem exce&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">VI </span></strong><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">- <strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">TEORIAS DAS RESPONSABILIDADES OBJETIVA E SUBJETIVA DO ESTADO E SUAS AUTARQUIAS.</strong></span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: black;"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Nesse aspecto, impende considerar a inexist&ecirc;ncia de culpa <em>in vigilando e in eligendo</em><span style="mso-bidi-font-style: italic;">, a ser atribu&iacute;da ao ente p&uacute;blico.</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>A culpa <em>in eligendo </em>se configuraria pela m&aacute; escolha do contratado; e a culpa <em>in vigilando, </em>pela aus&ecirc;ncia ou pela defici&ecirc;ncia na fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o do contrato administrativo.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>No que se refere &agrave; culpa i<em>n eligendo, </em><span style="mso-bidi-font-style: italic;">tem-se que</span> a transfer&ecirc;ncia de atividades da Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o para pessoas privadas obedece aos crit&eacute;rios estabelecidos em lei, mais precisamente na Lei de Licita&ccedil;&otilde;es e Contratos Administrativos (Lei n&ordm; 8.666/93), n&atilde;o estando o administrador autorizado a, discricionariamente, escolher a empresa licitante vencedora.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>O in&iacute;cio da participa&ccedil;&atilde;o dos candidatos no procedimento licitat&oacute;rio se d&aacute; com a habilita&ccedil;&atilde;o dos mesmos.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>E &eacute; exatamente nessa fase de habilita&ccedil;&atilde;o que as empresas interessadas dever&atilde;o comprovar a sua regularidade fiscal.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Dentre os documentos exigidos, comprobat&oacute;rios da regularidade fiscal, figura a "prova de regularidade relativa &agrave; Seguridade Social e ao Fundo de Garantia por Tempo de Servi&ccedil;o (FGTS), demonstrando situa&ccedil;&atilde;o regular no cumprimento dos encargos sociais institu&iacute;dos por lei."</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Assim, demonstrado, nessa fase, que a empresa n&atilde;o se encontra regular quanto ao cumprimento dos encargos sociais, ela &eacute;, desde logo, eliminada do certame.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>A partir da&iacute;, o procedimento licitat&oacute;rio segue sua habitual tramita&ccedil;&atilde;o at&eacute; o "julgamento e classifica&ccedil;&atilde;o das propostas de acordo com os crit&eacute;rios de avalia&ccedil;&atilde;o constantes do edital" (art. 43, V, da Lei 8.666/93).</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Reveste-se da maior import&acirc;ncia o teor do art. 50, da Lei 8.666/93:</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">"Art. 50. - A Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o n&atilde;o poder&aacute; celebrar o contrato com preteri&ccedil;&atilde;o da ordem de classifica&ccedil;&atilde;o das propostas ou com terceiros estranhos ao procedimento licitat&oacute;rio, sob pena de nulidade."<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: black;"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Como se v&ecirc;, n&atilde;o h&aacute; espa&ccedil;o para escolha, pelo administrador, da empresa contratada; os requisitos, para tal atua&ccedil;&atilde;o, constam da Lei 8.666/93, e o resultado obtido, atrav&eacute;s da incid&ecirc;ncia das regras disciplinadoras da esp&eacute;cie, sob hip&oacute;tese alguma, pode ser desobedecido.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Se a empresa, durante o procedimento licitat&oacute;rio, atendeu a todas as exig&ecirc;ncias legais, n&atilde;o h&aacute; raz&atilde;o para n&atilde;o ser contratada.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Agora, eventual descumprimento posterior, quanto ao pagamento dos encargos sociais, tratar-se-&aacute; de fato superveniente, que n&atilde;o se insere na &oacute;rbita de cautela da Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Observe-se, ademais, que deve, obrigatoriamente, constar do contrato administrativo, cl&aacute;usula que estabele&ccedil;a "a obriga&ccedil;&atilde;o do contratado de manter, durante toda a execu&ccedil;&atilde;o do contrato, em compatibilidade com as obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es por ele assumidas, todas as condi&ccedil;&otilde;es de habilita&ccedil;&atilde;o e qualifica&ccedil;&atilde;o exigidas na licita&ccedil;&atilde;o" (art. 55, XIII, da Lei 8.666/93).</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;">V&ecirc;-se, pois, que a obriga&ccedil;&atilde;o do contratado de manter a regularidade, no que toca aos encargos sociais, permanece durante toda a vig&ecirc;ncia do contrato administrativo, n&atilde;o restando qualquer responsabiliza&ccedil;&atilde;o da Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o, nesse aspecto.</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Afastada a tese da culpa <em>in eligendo, </em>passa-se &agrave; aprecia&ccedil;&atilde;o da responsabilidade do administrador em raz&atilde;o da aus&ecirc;ncia ou da defici&ecirc;ncia na fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o do contrato administrativo.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>A prerrogativa de fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o, atribu&iacute;da pela lei &agrave; Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica, se reporta t&atilde;o-somente &agrave; execu&ccedil;&atilde;o dos contratos administrativos.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Tal conclus&atilde;o ressoa da combina&ccedil;&atilde;o entre os arts. 58 e 67, &sect;1<sup>o</sup>., da Lei 8.666/93.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Segundo o art. 58, III, da Lei de Licita&ccedil;&otilde;es e dos Contratos Administrativos, "O regime jur&iacute;dico dos contratos administrativos institu&iacute;do por esta Lei confere &agrave; Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o, em rela&ccedil;&atilde;o a eles, a faculdade de: (...) III - fiscalizar-lhes a execu&ccedil;&atilde;o".</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Comentando este dispositivo, o Prof. Mar&ccedil;al Justen Filho informa que "Desse modo, verificar&aacute; se a realiza&ccedil;&atilde;o da presta&ccedil;&atilde;o faz-se nos termos devidos."<a style="mso-footnote-id: ftn4;" name="_ftnref4" href="#_ftn4"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="mso-ansi-font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%;"><span style="mso-special-character: footnote;"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">[4]</span></span></span></span></span></a></span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;">De acordo com o art. 67, &sect;1<sup>o</sup>., da Lei 8.666/93, acima reproduzido, verifica-se que o ente p&uacute;blico deve fiscalizar a execu&ccedil;&atilde;o do contrato administrativo, n&atilde;o os ajustes que a empresa contratada celebra com terceiros.</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>At&eacute; porque, conforme j&aacute; esclarecido, a empresa contratada &eacute; respons&aacute;vel pela manuten&ccedil;&atilde;o, durante a vig&ecirc;ncia do pacto, das condi&ccedil;&otilde;es de habilita&ccedil;&atilde;o e de qualifica&ccedil;&atilde;o exigidas na licita&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Assevere-se, ainda, que, na seq&uuml;&ecirc;ncia, a Lei 8.666/93, em seus arts. 68 e 69, se reporta &agrave; inser&ccedil;&atilde;o de preposto da contratada no local da obra ou servi&ccedil;o, para represent&aacute;-la na execu&ccedil;&atilde;o do contrato, e &agrave; responsabilidade da mesma empresa contratada pelos "v&iacute;cios, defeitos e incorre&ccedil;&otilde;es resultantes da execu&ccedil;&atilde;o".</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Da an&aacute;lise dos dispositivos mencionados, verifica-se a preocupa&ccedil;&atilde;o do legislador t&atilde;o-somente com a fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o da execu&ccedil;&atilde;o do objeto do contrato administrativo.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>V&ecirc;-se, portanto, que a fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o, a cargo da Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o, tem rela&ccedil;&atilde;o apenas com o objeto principal do contrato administrativo, no caso da terceiriza&ccedil;&atilde;o, com a efetiva presta&ccedil;&atilde;o dos servi&ccedil;os contratados.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>O &uacute;nico contrato, objeto de fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o, &eacute; o da presta&ccedil;&atilde;o de servi&ccedil;os; o ente p&uacute;blico, no decorrer da execu&ccedil;&atilde;o do contrato administrativo, n&atilde;o tem a obriga&ccedil;&atilde;o legal de fiscalizar se a empresa contratada honra os demais contratos, firmados com outras pessoas, f&iacute;sicas ou jur&iacute;dicas, ainda mais quando det&ecirc;m natureza privada.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 72.0pt; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Por outro lado, se, no contrato de trabalho tempor&aacute;rio, onde a intermedia&ccedil;&atilde;o da m&atilde;o-de-obra &eacute; l&iacute;cita (ver item I, da s&uacute;mula 331-TST), a fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o &eacute; realizada pelos &oacute;rg&atilde;os da fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o trabalhista (art. 15, da Lei 6.019, de 03.01.1974), porque exigir que, na terceiriza&ccedil;&atilde;o, ela seja feita pela entidade tomadora dos servi&ccedil;os?</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 144.0pt; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Nesse sentido, impende considerar a exist&ecirc;ncia da Instru&ccedil;&atilde;o Normativa n&ordm; 3 de 29.08.97., expedida pelo Minist&eacute;rio do Trabalho, que passou a cuidar da fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o do trabalho nas empresas de presta&ccedil;&atilde;o de servi&ccedil;os a terceiros e empresas de trabalho tempor&aacute;rio.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 144.0pt; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Assim, n&atilde;o restam d&uacute;vidas acerca da compet&ecirc;ncia do Minist&eacute;rio do Trabalho, atrav&eacute;s de seus Auditores/Fiscais, para fiscalizar o cumprimento das obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es trabalhistas pelas empresas terceirizadas.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">As raz&otilde;es expostas demonstram que as teses das culpas <em>in eligendo </em>e <em>in vigilando </em>n&atilde;o s&atilde;o suficientemente consistentes para imputar responsabilidade subsidi&aacute;ria a ente p&uacute;blico tomador de servi&ccedil;os pelos d&eacute;bitos trabalhistas pertencentes &agrave; empresa licitante contratada.</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Por &uacute;ltimo, merece realce, tamb&eacute;m, a inaplicabilidade da teoria da responsabilidade objetiva do </span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">DETRAN do RN<span style="color: black;"> prevista pelo art. 37, &sect;6<sup>o</sup>., da CF/88.</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 144.0pt; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">De fato, a pessoa jur&iacute;dica de direito p&uacute;blico, na hip&oacute;tese versada na s&uacute;mula n&ordm; 331, IV, do TST, n&atilde;o causou quaisquer danos a terceiros, em raz&atilde;o da atua&ccedil;&atilde;o de seus agentes, conforme exige o &sect;6<sup>o</sup>., do art. 37, da CF.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm;
