text-indent: 144.0pt; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Tamb&eacute;m deve ser salientado que o servi&ccedil;o, objeto do contrato administrativo, n&atilde;o pode ser considerado p&uacute;blico, pois n&atilde;o se insere na &oacute;rbita das atividades-fim da Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Conforme foi verificado, na terceiriza&ccedil;&atilde;o l&iacute;cita, somente os servi&ccedil;os que n&atilde;o se insiram nas atividades-fim do ente p&uacute;blico podem ser contratados.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 144.0pt; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Resta descaracterizada, portanto, a natureza p&uacute;blica dos servi&ccedil;os terceirizados.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 144.0pt; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Ainda, por&eacute;m, que se pudessem considerar p&uacute;blicos os servi&ccedil;os terceirizados, deve-se ter em mente que a pr&oacute;pria CF, no referido art. 37, &sect;6<sup>o</sup>., atribui &agrave;s pessoas jur&iacute;dicas de direito privado, prestadoras de servi&ccedil;o p&uacute;blico, a responsabilidade pelos danos causados a terceiros, por seus agentes, afastando, dessa forma, a responsabilidade do ente p&uacute;blico.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 144.0pt; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Finalmente, impende destacar que, nada obstante o </span></strong><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">DETRAN do RN<span style="color: black;"> seja o benefici&aacute;rio dos servi&ccedil;os prestados pelo empregado, nos casos de terceiriza&ccedil;&atilde;o, estes s&atilde;o devidamente pagos &agrave; empresa reclamada, j&aacute; que contratada atrav&eacute;s de licita&ccedil;&atilde;o, onde restou pactuado o valor referente n&atilde;o s&oacute; aos sal&aacute;rios daqueles, mas tamb&eacute;m a todos os encargos decorrentes do contrato laboral.</span></span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 144.0pt; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Condenar o </span></strong><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">DETRAN/RN<span style="color: black;">, com esteio nesse fundamento, significa <em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">bis in idem</em>, em claro preju&iacute;zo &agrave; sociedade, reais titulares da coisa p&uacute;blica.</span></span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 144.0pt; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Por qualquer &acirc;ngulo que se estude a responsabilidade objetiva, conclui-se pela sua inaplicabilidade sobre a terceiriza&ccedil;&atilde;o de servi&ccedil;os, no &acirc;mbito da Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica. </span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 144.0pt; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Como se v&ecirc;, quer pela &oacute;tica da responsabilidade subjetiva, quer pela da objetiva, inexiste a responsabilidade da Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica pelos d&eacute;bitos trabalhistas decorrentes do cumprimento de contrato administrativo.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal;"><strong><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">VII - VIOLA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O A PRECEITOS CONSTITUCIONAIS.</span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Observe-se que, ao aplicar o enunciado 331, IV, o julgado recorrido afastou a aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o de lei federal, sem que apontasse qualquer v&iacute;cio de inconstitucionalidade.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Ademais, por tratar-se de norma federal, o art. 71, &sect;1<sup>o</sup>., da Lei 8.666/93, somente poderia ser julgado inconstitucional, abstratamente, com efeito vinculante, pelo Supremo Tribunal Federal.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Assim, o TST negou vig&ecirc;ncia ao dispositivo legal acima referenciado atrav&eacute;s da edi&ccedil;&atilde;o de s&uacute;mula, fonte abstrata do direito, sem qualquer embasamento legal ou constitucional.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Recorreu apenas &agrave; sua jurisprud&ecirc;ncia.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Nesse aspecto, &eacute; de bom alvitre reproduzir os ensinamentos de F&aacute;bio Luiz de Ara&uacute;jo Rodrigues<a style="mso-footnote-id: ftn5;" name="_ftnref5" href="#_ftn5"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="mso-ansi-font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%;"><span style="mso-special-character: footnote;"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">[5]</span></span></span></span></span></a>:</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; text-indent: -.1pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">"Em contrapartida, n&atilde;o existe em nosso ordenamento jur&iacute;dico nenhum dispositivo legal ensejador da ora atacada responsabilidade subsidi&aacute;ria da administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica enquanto tomadora de servi&ccedil;os.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; text-indent: -.1pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">A nossa atual Magna Carta &eacute; bem clara ao afirmar em seu art. 5<sup>o</sup>., II, que:</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; text-indent: -.1pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">'II - ningu&eacute;m ser&aacute; obrigado a fazer ou deixar de fazer alguma coisa sen&atilde;o em virtude de lei;'</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; text-indent: -.1pt; line-height: normal;"><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">Por mais que o Direito do Trabalho seja eminentemente protetivo, a seguran&ccedil;a do trabalhador hipossuficiente n&atilde;o pode ser promovida ao arrepio da legisla&ccedil;&atilde;o federal.</span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; text-indent: -.1pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">(...)</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; text-indent: -.1pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">As s&uacute;mulas de orienta&ccedil;&atilde;o jurisprudencial s&atilde;o instrumentos eficazes para tra&ccedil;ar nortes aos operadores do Direito por demonstrarem a estes a forma com que determinado tribunal interpreta dispositivos legais. Contudo, <span style="text-decoration: underline;">jamais se pode admitir a utiliza&ccedil;&atilde;o de s&uacute;mulas com o intuito de negar aplicabilidade de dispositivo legal que se encontra plenamente em vigor.</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; text-indent: -.1pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">Ao agir desta forma, o Poder Judici&aacute;rio acaba por subtrair a fun&ccedil;&atilde;o de um dos outros tr&ecirc;s poderes da rep&uacute;blica, qual seja o Legislativo, a quem cabe precipuamente a fun&ccedil;&atilde;o de editar normas gerais e abstratas de conduta, as leis.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; text-indent: -.1pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">A Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o do TST n&ordm; 96/2000 configura evidente menoscabo a dois dos mais basilares princ&iacute;pios n&atilde;o s&oacute; da Rep&uacute;blica Federativa do Brasil como de qualquer Estado Democr&aacute;tico de Direito: o da legalidade, consoante j&aacute; exposto alhures, e o da triparti&ccedil;&atilde;o harm&ocirc;nica dos poderes Executivo, Legislativo e Judici&aacute;rio, por meio da consagrada f&oacute;rmula de freios e contrapesos nascida em meio ao iluminado pensamento de Montesquieu.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; text-indent: -.1pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">(...)" (grifos apostos)</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: black;"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Restou demonstrada, portanto, a afronta da s&uacute;mula 331-TST aos princ&iacute;pios constitucionais da legalidade e da independ&ecirc;ncia harm&ocirc;nica dos Poderes da Uni&atilde;o, estampados nos arts. 5<sup>o</sup>., II, 37, <em>caput, </em>e 2<sup>o</sup>., da CF/88.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Por oportuno, esclarece-se, ainda, a viola&ccedil;&atilde;o da s&uacute;mula sob an&aacute;lise ao princ&iacute;pio do contradit&oacute;rio e da ampla defesa.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Sim, pois o respectivo enunciado estabelece que a imputa&ccedil;&atilde;o da responsabilidade subsidi&aacute;ria se encontra subordinada &agrave; participa&ccedil;&atilde;o do ente p&uacute;blico na rela&ccedil;&atilde;o processual e na sua figura&ccedil;&atilde;o no t&iacute;tulo executivo judicial.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Ocorre que o ente p&uacute;blico n&atilde;o tem como ofertar defesa, em lides dessa natureza, haja vista o suposto reclamante nunca ter trabalhado para ele.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Com efeito, na terceiriza&ccedil;&atilde;o l&iacute;cita, como visto anteriormente, a dire&ccedil;&atilde;o da presta&ccedil;&atilde;o de servi&ccedil;os, o pagamento da remunera&ccedil;&atilde;o e dos demais direitos trabalhistas s&atilde;o obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es da empresa licitante vencedora.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Dessa forma, a condena&ccedil;&atilde;o da Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica sempre ocorre, sem que a mesma tenha qualquer argumento para invocar em ju&iacute;zo, haja vista o reclamante nunca ter prestado servi&ccedil;os a ela.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Da&iacute; decorre, tamb&eacute;m, a viola&ccedil;&atilde;o aos princ&iacute;pios constitucionais do contradit&oacute;rio e da ampla defesa, que figuram no art. 5<sup>o</sup>., LV, da CF/88.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Consoante se observa, o inciso IV, do enunciado 331 - TST, afronta especificamente princ&iacute;pios constitucionais fundamentais.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal;"><strong><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">VIII - DUPLA PENALIZA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O DO ENTE P&Uacute;BLICO CONTRATANTE.</span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Pelo fato de, por lei, a empresa prestadora de servi&ccedil;os ser unicamente respons&aacute;vel pelo pagamento dos encargos trabalhistas, afigura-se &oacute;bvio que as despesas com eles se encontram embutidas no pre&ccedil;o contratado com o ente p&uacute;blico.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Assim, n&atilde;o resta d&uacute;vida que a condena&ccedil;&atilde;o subsidi&aacute;ria da Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o, no pagamento de encargos trabalhistas decorrentes da execu&ccedil;&atilde;o de contrato administrativo de presta&ccedil;&atilde;o de servi&ccedil;os, significa o pagamento dobrado dos mesmos encargos, acarretando a dupla penaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o do ente p&uacute;blico contratante.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal;"><strong><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal;"><strong><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">IX - S&Uacute;MULA COMO FONTE INTERPRETATIVA DO DIREITO.</span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Passa-se, agora, a apreciar a real fun&ccedil;&atilde;o das s&uacute;mulas editadas pelos tribunais superiores, exceto a vinculante, de exclusiva compet&ecirc;ncia do Supremo Tribunal Federal, nos termos da Emenda Constitucional n&ordm; 45/2004.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>A jurisprud&ecirc;ncia, da qual decorrem as s&uacute;mulas dos tribunais, se apresenta como fonte de interpreta&ccedil;&atilde;o do direito.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Segundo li&ccedil;&atilde;o do Professor Miguel Reale<a style="mso-footnote-id: ftn6;" name="_ftnref6" href="#_ftn6"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="mso-ansi-font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%;"><span style="mso-special-character: footnote;"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">[6]</span></span></span></span></span></a>, "Em tese, os tribunais s&atilde;o chamados a aplicar a lei e a revelar o Direito sempre atrav&eacute;s de lei."</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Mas as s&uacute;mulas dos tribunais n&atilde;o podem chegar ao absurdo de negar vig&ecirc;ncia &agrave; lei sem apontar a exist&ecirc;ncia de v&iacute;cios insan&aacute;veis.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>A vig&ecirc;ncia de uma norma, no caso o &sect;1<sup>o</sup>., do art. 71, da Lei 8.666/93, n&atilde;o pode ser negada apenas pelo fato do TST se posicionar contrariamente ao seu teor; a sua aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o somente pode ser afastada na hip&oacute;tese de contar com v&iacute;cios formais e/ou materiais dos quais decorram sua invalidade no mundo jur&iacute;dico.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp;</span>O Professor L&ecirc;nio Luiz Streck<a style="mso-footnote-id: ftn7;" name="_ftnref7" href="#_ftn7"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="mso-ansi-font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%;"><span style="mso-special-character: footnote;"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">[7]</span></span></span></span></span></a> emite alerta &agrave; m&aacute; utiliza&ccedil;&atilde;o das s&uacute;mulas pelos tribunais, esclarecendo que "Na pr&aacute;tica, por&eacute;m, as S&uacute;mulas passaram a ter valor superior &agrave;s pr&oacute;prias leis, sendo que, em muitos casos, muito al&eacute;m de serem interpretativas das normas vigentes, passam a ser (...) <em>fontes criadoras de leis, </em>editadas contra as leis vigentes (s&uacute;mulas <em>contra legem</em>) e contra a Constitui&ccedil;&atilde;o Federal (s&uacute;mulas inconstitucionais)."</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>E foi exatamente nesse contexto que ocorreu a edi&ccedil;&atilde;o da s&uacute;mula 331-TST, ou seja, com viola&ccedil;&atilde;o direta &agrave; legisla&ccedil;&atilde;o e &agrave; Constitui&ccedil;&atilde;o Federais, pr&aacute;tica essa que deve ser repudiada pelo nosso ordenamento jur&iacute;dico.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Nesse aspecto, faz-se oportuno reproduzir a li&ccedil;&atilde;o de Fernando dos Santos Wilges<a style="mso-footnote-id: ftn8;" name="_ftnref8" href="#_ftn8"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="mso-ansi-font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%;"><span style="mso-special-character: footnote;"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">[8]</span></span></span></span></span></a>:</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black; mso-bidi-font-style: italic;">"Ora, um Enunciado, conceituado como a ementa que revela a orienta&ccedil;&atilde;o jurisprudencial de um tribunal para casos an&aacute;logos, sendo portanto um dos resultados da produ&ccedil;&atilde;o jurisprudencial, constitui-se em fonte formal estatal do direito. Sendo assim est&aacute; abaixo da Lei Federal. Estando abaixo, n&atilde;o pode contrari&aacute;-la, sob hip&oacute;tese alguma."</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black; background: lime; mso-highlight: lime;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black; background: lime; mso-highlight: lime;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal;"><strong><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">X - VIOLA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O AO ART. 8&ordm;. DA CONSOLIDA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O DAS LEIS DO TRABALHO.</span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: black;"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">&Agrave; derradeira, evidencia-se a afronta, pela S&uacute;mula 331-TST, ao teor do art. 8<sup>o</sup>., da Consolida&ccedil;&atilde;o das Leis do Trabalho, cujo teor passa-se a transcrever:</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black; mso-bidi-font-style: italic;">"Art. 8<sup>o</sup>. - As autoridades administrativas e a Justi&ccedil;a do Trabalho, na falta de disposi&ccedil;&otilde;es legais ou contratuais, decidir&atilde;o, conforme o caso, pela jurisprud&ecirc;ncia, por analogia, por equidade e outros princ&iacute;pios e normas gerais do direito, principalmente do direito do trabalho, e, ainda, de acordo com os usos e costumes, o direito comparado, mas sempre de maneira que nenhum interesse de classe ou particular prevale&ccedil;a sobre o interesse p&uacute;blico."</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: black; background: lime; mso-highlight: lime;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: black;"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">O texto &eacute; claro, quando afirma a impossibilidade de se fazer prevalecer o interesse particular sobre o interesse p&uacute;blico, em se tratando de aus&ecirc;ncia de disposi&ccedil;&atilde;o legal disciplinadora da mat&eacute;ria submetida &agrave; aprecia&ccedil;&atilde;o judicial.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Trazendo tais determina&ccedil;&otilde;es para o tema ora analisado, verifica-se que existe lei, isentando o ente p&uacute;blico quanto ao pagamento dos encargos trabalhistas decorrentes da execu&ccedil;&atilde;o de contrato administrativo, e, nada obstante isso, a Justi&ccedil;a Trabalhista, atrav&eacute;s de sua mais alta corte, estabelece que os interesses dos trabalhadores, prestadores de servi&ccedil;os terceirizados, devem se sobrepor aos da Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica, encarregada do bem-estar dos cidad&atilde;os e, portanto, maior representante dos interesses p&uacute;blicos.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Dessa forma, n&atilde;o resta d&uacute;vida acerca da desobedi&ecirc;ncia, pelo entendimento sumular, aos termos do art. 8<sup>o</sup>., acima reproduzido.</span></p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; tab-stops: 5.0cm;"><strong><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"><strong><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">XI - </span></strong><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">DA DESCONSIDERA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O DA PERSONALIDADE JUR&Iacute;DICA DA EMPRESA RECLAMADA - MAT&Eacute;RIA DE ORDEM P&Uacute;BLICA - IMPOSI&Ccedil;&Atilde;O DOS PRINC&Iacute;PIOS DA LEGALIDADE E MORALIDADE.</span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 5.0cm;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Embora sustente que n&atilde;o tem, ou n&atilde;o deva ter qualquer responsabilidade pelo suposto inadimplemento da Reclamada principal, pelas raz&otilde;es j&aacute; elencadas, suscita, novamente, mat&eacute;ria de ordem p&uacute;blica.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 5.0cm;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Aqui n&atilde;o se trata de querer o </span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">DETRAN do RN<span style="color: black;"> exercer o seu direito de a&ccedil;&atilde;o regressiva contra a empresa prestadora de servi&ccedil;os, mas sim, de chamar &agrave; lide os s&oacute;cios desta para que, ao integrarem o p&oacute;lo passivo da a&ccedil;&atilde;o, possam ser responsabilizados patrimonialmente antes da imputa&ccedil;&atilde;o de responsabilidade ao </span>DETRAN do RN<span style="color: black;">.</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 5.0cm;"><span style="font-size: 9.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: black;"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">O que se pretende, dessa forma, &eacute; evitar que os s&oacute;cios e a pessoa jur&iacute;dica se locupletem &agrave; custa do Estado e de suas autarquias e de suas autarquias e at&eacute; do empregado, pois foram os s&oacute;cios os benefici&aacute;rios diretos do resultado do trabalho do obreiro.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 5.0cm;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Entende o </span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">DETRAN do RN<span style="color: black;"> que, na hip&oacute;tese de a Reclamada n&atilde;o dispor de dinheiro ou patrim&ocirc;nio para honrar eventual obriga&ccedil;&atilde;o para com o Reclamante, seus s&oacute;cios devem ser chamados &agrave; lide na qualidade de co-obrigados.</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 3;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Al&eacute;m de &eacute;tico, moral e leg&iacute;timo, esse pleito &eacute; juridicamente poss&iacute;vel. N&atilde;o tem cunho protelat&oacute;rio e se consegue proteger o direito do trabalhador e, ao mesmo tempo, preservar os interesses, direitos e patrim&ocirc;nio do Estado/autarquias.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 3;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>&Eacute; cedi&ccedil;o que atualmente &eacute; pac&iacute;fica a doutrina e a jurisprud&ecirc;ncia quanto &agrave; aplicabilidade da <strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">disregard of legal entity (despersonaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o da personalidade jur&iacute;dica)</em></strong> no Direito Civil, Comercial e nas rela&ccedil;&otilde;es de consumo. &Eacute; poss&iacute;vel e aceit&aacute;vel que tamb&eacute;m se aplique a desconsidera&ccedil;&atilde;o da personalidade jur&iacute;dica no &acirc;mbito do Direito do Trabalho.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 3;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Se a empresa n&atilde;o paga, antes de se responsabilizar o </span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">DETRAN do RN<span style="color: black;">, a Justi&ccedil;a deve responsabilizar os s&oacute;cios da empresa. Muitas vezes, as empresas se encontram em situa&ccedil;&atilde;o dif&iacute;cil, algumas at&eacute; falidas. Todavia, esta situa&ccedil;&atilde;o &eacute; economicamente muito mais vantajosa para seus s&oacute;cios. Tal fato constitui-se desvio da fun&ccedil;&atilde;o da pessoa jur&iacute;dica, que pode ser constatado mediante fraude e/ou abuso de direito relativos &agrave; sua autonomia patrimonial da sociedade.</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 3;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>A responsabilidade patrimonial se afigura um instituto do direito material, porque decorrente da rela&ccedil;&atilde;o obrigacional, mas tamb&eacute;m ser&aacute; um instituto de direito processual, quando necess&aacute;rio <strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">o chamamento dos s&oacute;cios, ainda no processo de conhecimento</span></strong>, para que se defenda e, depois, possa responder com seu patrim&ocirc;nio.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 3;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Dessa forma, a Justi&ccedil;a do Trabalho n&atilde;o pode compactuar com uma dupla penaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o do Estado/AUTARQUIAS. No dia que a Justi&ccedil;a do Trabalho come&ccedil;ar a responsabilizar os s&oacute;cios das empresas, a&iacute; sim, pode-se ter certeza, os s&oacute;cios v&atilde;o pensar duas vezes antes de lesar o trabalhador.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 3;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>O art. 591 do CPC imp&otilde;e a responsabilidade patrimonial do devedor atrav&eacute;s de seus bens. O fundamento jur&iacute;dico justificador da constri&ccedil;&atilde;o do patrim&ocirc;nio do devedor a satisfazer a obriga&ccedil;&atilde;o decorre da rela&ccedil;&atilde;o jur&iacute;dica obrigacional, composta de 2 (dois) elementos: o <em>d&eacute;bito</em>, de natureza de direito material e a <em>responsabilidade</em>, de natureza processual. Essa diferencia&ccedil;&atilde;o entre d&iacute;vida e responsabilidade &eacute; fundamental quando se pretende estabelecer a possibilidade de alcance de patrim&ocirc;nio de terceiro, atrav&eacute;s da doutrina da desconsidera&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 3;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>A doutrina adverte, com raz&atilde;o, que d&iacute;vida n&atilde;o se confunde com responsabilidade. S&atilde;o figuras jur&iacute;dicas distintas. A d&iacute;vida &eacute; pessoal, vinculando no Direito do Trabalho o empregado e o empregador. J&aacute; a responsabilidade vincula o cr&eacute;dito exequendo com o patrim&ocirc;nio do devedor (executado), mas com a diferen&ccedil;a que essa "pessoa exigida"<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>poder&aacute; ser o devedor ou terceiros respons&aacute;veis, seja em decorr&ecirc;ncia de normas legais, seja em face da aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o da doutrina da desconsidera&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 3;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>N&atilde;o se deve olvidar que os artigos 591 e 592 do CPC estabelecem que o devedor responde, para cumprimento de suas obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es, com todos os bens presentes e futuros. <strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Tamb&eacute;m ficam sujeitos &agrave; execu&ccedil;&atilde;o os bens dos s&oacute;cios</span></strong>.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 3;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>A doutrina da desconsidera&ccedil;&atilde;o dirige-se &agrave; <strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">responsabilidade patrimonial secund&aacute;ria</span></strong>, nos casos onde n&atilde;o houve previs&atilde;o legal do alcance do patrim&ocirc;nio de terceiros. A CLT tratou da responsabilidade patrimonial nos artigos 876 a 892. Contudo, embora omissa quanto &agrave; responsabilidade secund&aacute;ria, deve-se aplicar subsidiariamente os arts. 591 e 597 do CPC que tratam de execu&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 3;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>O art. 592 do CPC disp&otilde;e que ficam sujeitos &agrave; execu&ccedil;&atilde;o os bens:</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 125.4pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 16.2pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black; mso-bidi-font-style: italic;">"I - do sucessor a t&iacute;tulo singular;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 109.2pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 32.4pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black; mso-bidi-font-style: italic;">II - do s&oacute;cio, nos termos da lei;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 125.4pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 16.2pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black; mso-bidi-font-style: italic;">III - do devedor, quando em poder de terceiros;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 141.6pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black; mso-bidi-font-style: italic;">IV - do c&ocirc;njuge, nos casos em que os seus bens pr&oacute;prios, reservados ou de sua mea&ccedil;&atilde;o respondem pela d&iacute;vida;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 125.4pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 16.2pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black; mso-bidi-font-style: italic;">V - alienados ou gravados com &ocirc;nus real em fraude de execu&ccedil;&atilde;o."</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%;"><em><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">&nbsp;</span></em></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 70.9pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 3;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Em Semin&aacute;rio realizado em 21 de agosto de 2006 na sede da Confedera&ccedil;&atilde;o Nacional da Ind&uacute;stria (CNI), o ent&atilde;o Ministro do TST proferiu palestra sobre o tema <strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">"Desconsidera&ccedil;&atilde;o da Personalidade Jur&iacute;dica e Responsabilidade Direta de S&oacute;cios e Administradores: Uso e Abuso</strong>", onde defendeu a tese da necessidade de se aplicar a desconsidera&ccedil;&atilde;o da personalidade jur&iacute;dica no Direito do Trabalho(Cf.em<a href="http://ext02.tst.gov.br/pls/no01/no_noticias.Exibe_Noticia?p_cod_noticia=6817&amp;p_cod_area_noticia=ASCS"><span style="color: black;">http://ext02.tst.gov.br/pls/no01/no_noticias.Exibe_Noticia?p_cod_noticia=6817&amp;p_cod_area_noticia=ASCS</span></a>).</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 70.9pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 3;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Ali&aacute;s, nesse mesmo evento, a Ministra Cristina Peduzzi, do TST, reafirmou a necessidade de aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o da desconsidera&ccedil;&atilde;o da personalidade jur&iacute;dica e citou decis&otilde;es da Justi&ccedil;a do Trabalho para ilustrar as diversas formas pela qual tal princ&iacute;pio vem sendo aplicado. <strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">"A tend&ecirc;ncia tem sido a de responsabilizar pessoalmente o s&oacute;cio mesmo quando n&atilde;o configurado o abuso ou a fraude"</strong>, disse sua Excel&ecirc;ncia.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 70.9pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 3;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Se no processo de conhecimento se vislumbra, por qualquer raz&atilde;o, a empresa Reclamada como inid&ocirc;nea economicamente (pode-se tomar como refer&ecirc;ncia, Por exemplo, elevado n&uacute;mero de Reclama&ccedil;&otilde;es Trabalhistas ajuizadas), antes de se decidir acerca da responsabiliza&ccedil;&atilde;o do </span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">DETRAN do RN<span style="color: black;">, <strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">devem os s&oacute;cios ser chamados a responder pelas obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es trabalhistas inadimplidas</span></strong>, inclusive respondendo com seus patrim&ocirc;nios pessoais. Isso n&atilde;o causa risco nenhum ao empregado e protege o patrim&ocirc;nio p&uacute;blico. Cabe registrar que isso &eacute; juridicamente poss&iacute;vel porque o direcionamento da a&ccedil;&atilde;o contra bens pesoais dos s&oacute;cios da Reclamada encontra s&oacute;lido respaldo nas disposi&ccedil;&otilde;es do art. 10 do Decreto 3.708/19, que regula as sociedades por quotas de responsabilidade limitada<span style="text-decoration: underline;">, sempre que constatada a ocorr&ecirc;ncia de atos praticados com viola&ccedil;&atilde;o da lei ou do contrato</span>, hip&oacute;tese na qual se insere, indiscutivelmente, a infring&ecirc;ncia de preceitos da legisla&ccedil;&atilde;o trabalhista. Nesse mesmo sentido, pode ser invocado, analogicamente, o disposto no art. 135 do CTN e no artigo 4o. da Lei 6.830/80. (Ver, a respeito, Ac&oacute;rd&atilde;o n&ordm; 19990432158, Turma: 8a. TRT/SP, Data julg. 05.08.99, Data de Pub.: 14.09.99, Processo: 02980577850, Relatora: Wilma Nogueira de Ara&uacute;jo Vaz da Silva).</span></span></p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><strong><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Por fim, importa fazer uma breve inquiri&ccedil;&atilde;o: se n&atilde;o houvesse a garantia de pagamento pelo Estado/AUTARQUIAS - atrav&eacute;s da subsidiariedade - a Justi&ccedil;a n&atilde;o iria atingir o patrim&ocirc;nio pessoal dos s&oacute;cios para pagamento das d&iacute;vidas trabalhistas da sociedade? Evidente que sim, e, ressalte-se, que a teoria da desconsidera&ccedil;&atilde;o da personalidade jur&iacute;dica vem sendo aplicada h&aacute; bastante tempo na Justi&ccedil;a do Trabalho, em garantia dos direitos dos empregados. </span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 70.9pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: black;"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="mso-tab-count: 2;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Assim, somente ap&oacute;s excutidos todos os bens da empresa e de seus s&oacute;cios &eacute; que o ente p&uacute;blico poder&aacute; ser acionado para fazer frente aos cr&eacute;ditos trabalhistas.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 70.9pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 3;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Em face do exposto, requer o DETRAN/RN o re</span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">conhecimento da quest&atilde;o de ordem p&uacute;blica ora suscitada e chame &agrave; lide, como <strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">co-obrigados/devedores solid&aacute;rios</span></strong>, j&aacute; agora no processo de conhecimento, as pessoas dos s&oacute;cios da empresa <strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">reclamada principal.</strong></span></p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 144.0pt; line-height: 150%; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Requer-se, portanto, a aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o do que estabelece o art. 50, do novo C&oacute;digo Civil Brasileiro.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">XII - DA CONDENA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O NAS MULTAS DO ART. 467 E 477, DA CLT, DAS HORAS EXTRAS, DA INDENIZACAO PELA N&Atilde;O DEVOLUCAO DA CTPS</span></strong><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">.</span></strong></p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 144.0pt; line-height: 150%; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"><span style="font-size: 12.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 144.0pt; line-height: 150%; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Mister registrar, de logo, a improced&ecirc;ncia do pagamento da multa do art. 467 consolidado. De fato, o pagamento dos t&iacute;tulos trabalhistas, com rela&ccedil;&atilde;o ao litisconsorte passivo, &eacute; questionado, &eacute; controvertido, e o ente p&uacute;blico tem se irresignado contra o pagamento de qualquer parcela que seja, desde o in&iacute;cio da rela&ccedil;&atilde;o processual. Se a empresa reclamada principal admitir a aus&ecirc;ncia de controv&eacute;rsia quanto ao direito do reclamante aos t&iacute;tulos trabalhistas, que a ela seja aplicada a multa do art. 467, da CLT. Com rela&ccedil;&atilde;o ao litisconsorte, contudo, ela n&atilde;o pode ser aplicada, pois o mesmo afirma o descabimento de sua condena&ccedil;&atilde;o e ir&aacute; discuti-lo at&eacute; as inst&acirc;ncias extraordin&aacute;rias (TST e STF).</span></p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 144.0pt; line-height: 150%; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">A multa do art. 477, da CLT, n&atilde;o pode ser aplicada aos entes p&uacute;blicos, haja vista o pagamento dos servidores estaduais, por exemplo, somente ocorrer no final do m&ecirc;s, e a folha de pagamento fechar no dia oito de cada m&ecirc;s. Assim, n&atilde;o h&aacute; como assegurar o imediato pagamento de contratos rescindidos, inclusive, porque o ente p&uacute;blico recorrente n&atilde;o conta com empregados celetistas em seus quadros. Ademais, qualquer pagamento a ser realizado pelos &oacute;rg&atilde;os p&uacute;blicos demanda uma tramita&ccedil;&atilde;o administrativa burocr&aacute;tica, prevista em lei.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="text-indent: 5.0cm; tab-stops: 138.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Nos termos do que preconizam os arts. 818, da CLT e 373, I do CPC, cabe ao reclamante provar os fatos constitutivos de seu direito, quanto &agrave;s verbas postuladas e eventualmente n&atilde;o percebidas.</span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "> </span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="text-indent: 5.0cm; tab-stops: 138.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Como se percebe, o demandante apenas acosta c&oacute;pia parcial de sua CTPS, e nesta sequer consta qualquer refer&ecirc;ncia ao contrato com a empresa reclamada.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="text-indent: 5.0cm; tab-stops: 138.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Ademais, os documentos anexados aos autos n&atilde;o s&atilde;o aptos a provar que o autor n&atilde;o recebeu as verbas rescis&oacute;rias que alega fazer jus, eis que apenas adunou tr&ecirc;s recibos de pagamento, referentes aos meses de julho, agosto e novembro de 2017. <span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="text-indent: 5.0cm; tab-stops: 138.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Assim, como n&atilde;o se desincumbiu do <span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp;</span>mister de provar os fatos constitutivos de seu direito - vinculo laboral, data de in&iacute;cio e de finaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o do contrato - seu pleito deveria ter sido, <em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">m.d.v.,</em> julgado improcedente. <span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyText"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 4;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Quanto &agrave;s horas extras - referente &agrave; supress&atilde;o do intervalo intrajornada -<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>o &ocirc;nus da prova e do reclamante, nos termos do que vaticinam os arts. 818, da CLT e 373, I, do CPC.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>Observe-se, ainda, que nos termos da atrial, o reclamante informa que consignava em seu ponto di&aacute;rio o citado intervalo. </span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="text-indent: 141.6pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Nesse sentido, segue a pac&iacute;fica jurisprud&ecirc;ncia obreira, Veja-se:</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="text-indent: 144.0pt; tab-stops: 233.25pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; background: yellow; mso-highlight: yellow; font-weight: normal;">HORAS EXTRAS - PROVA - Sendo a sobrejornada exce&ccedil;&atilde;o &agrave; regra da jornada normal, torna-se imprescind&iacute;vel a prova, pois a presun&ccedil;&atilde;o elucida apenas os fatos normais. Tal &ocirc;nus era do autor (arts. 818 da CLT e 333, I, do CPC), do qual, todavia, n&atilde;o logrou se desincumbir satisfatoriamente. Recurso n&atilde;o provido. (TRT 10&ordf; R. - RO 2775/2001 - 2&ordf; T. - Rel&ordf; Ju&iacute;za Helo&iacute;sa Pinto Marques - DJU 22.02.2002 - p. 148)</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; background: yellow; mso-highlight: yellow; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; background: yellow; mso-highlight: yellow; font-weight: normal;">HORAS EXTRAS - PROVA - Quando negada na defesa a presta&ccedil;&atilde;o de trabalho extraordin&aacute;rio, &eacute; do empregado o &ocirc;nus da prova, nos termos do art. 818 da CLT. (TRT 12&ordf; R. - RO-V . 10762/2001 - (02781/2002) - Florian&oacute;polis - 1&ordf; T. - Rel. Juiz Garibaldi T. P. Ferreira - J. 20.03.2002)</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; background: yellow; mso-highlight: yellow; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; background: yellow; mso-highlight: yellow; font-weight: normal;">HORAS EXTRAS - PROVA - &Eacute; do trabalhador o &ocirc;nus da prova objetiva do trabalho extraordin&aacute;rio sem a devida paga, n&atilde;o podendo o direito em quest&atilde;o ser acolhido por presun&ccedil;&otilde;es ou dedu&ccedil;&otilde;es - art. 818 da CLT. (TRT 15&ordf; R. - Proc. 14709/00 - (13332/02) - 1&ordf; T. - Rel. Juiz Luiz Antonio Lazarim - DOESP 08.04.2002 - p. 55).</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; background: yellow; mso-highlight: yellow; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="background: yellow; mso-highlight: yellow;">Perceba-se que, nada obstante a revelia da reclamada principal, cabia ao magistrado, tendo em vista o interesse p&uacute;blico envolvido - demanda em face de ente p&uacute;blico - e, ainda, o princ&iacute;pio da verdade real, ter procedido &agrave; instru&ccedil;&atilde;o, com oitiva do reclamante e de testemunhas, com vistas a corroborar ou n&atilde;o a supress&atilde;o do intervalo intrajornada.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 144.0pt; line-height: 150%;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Portanto, a senten&ccedil;a incidiu em <em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;">error in procedendo</em>, sobretudo no que tange ao deferimento de horas extras sem a devida instru&ccedil;&atilde;o processual.</span></strong><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 144.0pt; line-height: 150%; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">No caso dos autos, descabe a condena&ccedil;&atilde;o subsidi&aacute;ria do recorrente no que toca &agrave;s contribui&ccedil;&otilde;es previdenci&aacute;rias, que t&ecirc;m natureza tribut&aacute;ria, haja vista a s&uacute;mula 331, em seu inciso IV, estabelecer a responsabilidade subsidi&aacute;ria unicamente quanto &agrave;s obriga&ccedil;&otilde;es trabalhistas</span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyTextIndent2" style="margin-left: 0cm; tab-stops: 144.0pt 216.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">XIII - DA LIMITA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O.</span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Na improv&aacute;vel hip&oacute;tese de condena&ccedil;&atilde;o do DETRAN (NO QUE N&Atilde;O SE ACREDITA), requer-se, desde logo, a limita&ccedil;&atilde;o da mesma ao per&iacute;odo em que restar demonstrado que a reclamante, <strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">efetivamente</strong>, prestou servi&ccedil;os, em decorr&ecirc;ncia de terceiriza&ccedil;&atilde;o do contrato de trabalho, ao ente p&uacute;blico.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>De fato, pode ficar comprovado que a demandante n&atilde;o prestou servi&ccedil;o terceirizado ao ente p&uacute;blico durante todo o per&iacute;odo delimitado na exordial, mas sim em interst&iacute;cio inferior.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="line-height: normal; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: "><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">XIV - DOS PEDIDOS</span></p>\n<p class="MsoBodyText" style="line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: black; font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 150%; color: black;"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Por todo exposto, requer o </span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">DETRAN/RN<span style="color: black;"> a reforma do julgado de primeira inst&acirc;ncia, para que ocorra:</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 1.2pt; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list -9.0pt left 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">a)<span style="font: 7.0pt ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">preliminarmente, o reconhecimento da incompet&ecirc;ncia <em>in ratione materiae</em> da Justi&ccedil;a do Trabalho para apreciar as conseq&uuml;&ecirc;ncias jur&iacute;dicas advindas de contrato estritamente administrativo, firmado entre ente p&uacute;blico e empresa privada, com a conseq&uuml;ente extin&ccedil;&atilde;o do feito, sem julgamento do m&eacute;rito, no que se refere ao </span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">DETRAN/ RN<span style="color: black;">;</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 1.2pt; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list -9.0pt left 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">b)<span style="font: 7.0pt ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">preliminarmente, sua exclus&atilde;o da lide, em face de sua patente ilegitimidade passiva <em>ad causam;</em></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 1.2pt; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list -9.0pt left 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">c)<span style="font: 7.0pt ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">no m&eacute;rito, a n&atilde;o aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o do Enunciado n&ordm; 331 do TST, sobre a esp&eacute;cie dos autos, </span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">reconhecendo-se a inexist&ecirc;ncia da responsabilidade subsidi&aacute;ria estatal;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 1.2pt; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list -9.0pt left 144.0pt;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">d)<span style="font: 7.0pt ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></strong><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">a condena&ccedil;&atilde;o unicamente da reclamada principal no pagamento das verbas consignadas em senten&ccedil;a, <strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">notadamente, em raz&atilde;o do novel entendimento do e. STF;</strong></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 1.2pt; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list -9.0pt left 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">e)<span style="font: 7.0pt ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">a decreta&ccedil;&atilde;o da total improced&ecirc;ncia da pretens&atilde;o autoral;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 1.2pt; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list -9.0pt left 144.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">f)<span style="font: 7.0pt ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">a condena&ccedil;&atilde;o da recorrida no pagamento dos &ocirc;nus da sucumb&ecirc;ncia;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 1.2pt; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list -9.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">g)<span style="font: 7.0pt ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">a compensa&ccedil;&atilde;o de todos os valores que tenham sido ou venham a ser adimplidos ao recorrido at&eacute; o final de eventual processo de execu&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 1.2pt; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: list -9.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">Natal, 14 de novembro de 2018.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 144.0pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-indent: 1.2pt; line-height: 150%; tab-stops: list -9.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: ">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<h2 style="text-align: center; text-indent: 35.4pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: ">TEREZA CRISTINA RAMALHO TEIXEIRA</span></h2>\n<h1 style="text-align: center; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 9.0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: "><span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Procuradora do Estado</span></h1>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;" align="center"><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; margin-right: 2.45pt; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 4.0cm; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;"><span style="font-family: ">ESTE DOUTO JU&Iacute;ZO DEVE ABANDONAR A POSI&Ccedil;&Atilde;O DE SIMPLESMENTE SUPOR CULPA DO PODER P&Uacute;BLICO POR AUS&Ecirc;NCIA DE FISCALIZA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O DOS CONTRATOS FIRMADOS, ALOCANDO-O COMO FIADOR DAS REFERIDAS EMPRESAS, MISTER DEPOIS DO FIRMADO PELO STF EM TESE DE REPERCUSS&Atilde;O GERAL. </span></em></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoNormalCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top: 6.0pt; margin-right: 2.45pt; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 4.0cm; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;"><span style="font-family: ">&nbsp;</span></em></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoNormalCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top: 6.0pt; margin-right: 2.45pt; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 4.0cm; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;"><span style="font-family: ">COM EFEITO, TAL COMO DECIDIDO PELA CORTE CONSTITUCIONAL, H&Aacute; QUE SE INVERTER O &Ocirc;NUS PROBAT&Oacute;RIO DE TAL OMISS&Atilde;O, CABENDO AGORA AO RECLAMANTE E N&Atilde;O AO RECLAMADO, CONFORME PRETENDE O INSIGNE JU&Iacute;ZO SENTENCIANTE.</span></em></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoNormalCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top: 6.0pt; margin-right: 2.45pt; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0cm; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 1.0cm; line-height: normal;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="font-family: "><span style="text-decoration: none;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoNormalCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top: 6.0pt; margin-right: 2.45pt; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 4.0cm; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 72.0pt;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="font-family: ">N&atilde;o h&aacute; qualquer documenta&ccedil;&atilde;o acostada nos autos que comprove a rela&ccedil;&atilde;o contratual entre a demandada principal e o Estado do RN, e cabia &agrave; reclamante o &ocirc;nus de provar suas alega&ccedil;&otilde;es, nos termos do que determina o art. 373, I, do CPC e o art. 818, I, da CLT!</span></span></strong><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoNormalCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top: 6.0pt; margin-right: 2.45pt; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 4.0cm; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 72.0pt;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="font-family: "><span style="text-decoration: none;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoNormalCxSpMiddle" style="margin-top: 6.0pt; margin-right: 2.45pt; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 4.0cm; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 72.0pt;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="font-family: ">Ademais, as exig&ecirc;ncias de fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o foram cumpridas, n&atilde;o merecendo invers&atilde;o do &ocirc;nus da prova e acatamento do pleito autoral.</span></span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; line-height: 150%;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-family: ">RESUMO DOS FATOS</span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 1.0cm; line-height: 150%; mso-pagination: none; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: "><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">1.<span style="font: 7.0pt ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
